4.11	Gettysburg_(game)	Gettysburg (game)	Gettysburg is a board wargame produced by Avalon Hill which re-enacts the American Civil War battle of Gettysburg. It was originally published in 1958, and was the first board wargame based on a historical battle.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c6/Gettysburg_Board_Game_1958.jpg/200px-Gettysburg_Board_Game_1958.jpg
